Mother,

273
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:18,150
but I simply don't like him.

274
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:19,480
You're a woman, too.

275
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:21,630
Can't you understand how I feel?

276
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:23,630
I don't care.

277
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:25,320
I just wanna be together with Sha Pingwei.

278
00:15:25,670 --> 00:15:26,550
I love him.

279
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:44,910
You were just like me when I was young.

280
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:47,320
A silly girl

281
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:50,360
who believes in love.

282
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:54,840
But when you finally grow up someday,

283
00:15:55,440 --> 00:15:56,480
you'll see

284
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:59,600
that this is nothing but a fantasy.

285
00:15:59,790 --> 00:16:01,120
It is not reliable.

286
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:08,120
Had I realized this earlier...

287
00:16:14,510 --> 00:16:15,240
Mother,

288
00:16:15,790 --> 00:16:18,360
you often stare at this portrait.

289
00:16:18,790 --> 00:16:21,000
What exactly happened back then?

290
00:16:22,270 --> 00:16:23,960
Just some sad things.

291
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:29,670
I look at this portrait every day

292
00:16:31,390 --> 00:16:33,150
just to remind myself

293
00:16:34,870 --> 00:16:36,670
not to abandon myself to emotion

294
00:16:38,750 --> 00:16:39,960
like I did before.

295
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:41,670
Mother,

296
00:16:41,870 --> 00:16:43,440
but I just wanna know...

297
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:44,510
I'm tired.

298
00:16:46,510 --> 00:16:48,120
You should go back to rest now.

299
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:50,870
Mother.

300
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:54,200
No more discussion.

301
00:16:55,870 --> 00:16:56,910
This thing is settled.

302
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:01,270
Then I'll take my leave.

303
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:41,590
Your Majesty,

304
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:44,160
Yuan Buqu is known
for his military merits.

305
00:17:44,790 --> 00:17:48,790
His Majesty is letting him
lead the imperial guards and the armies.

306
00:17:49,070 --> 00:17:50,350
If you push him like this,

307
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:53,310
aren't you afraid that he'll rebel?

308
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,200
The military power

309
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:57,350
hasn't been handed over to him, has it?

310
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:01,200
Besides, the wine today

311
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:03,590
wasn't really poisonous.

312
00:18:05,070 --> 00:18:05,920
This is but

313
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:07,310
a strategy

314
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:10,070
to kill two birds with one stone.

315
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,480
There's a personal reason.

316
00:18:13,920 --> 00:18:14,830
Changping

317
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:17,310
is still childlike.

318
00:18:17,790 --> 00:18:19,110
I wanted to test

319
00:18:19,830 --> 00:18:21,200
if Changping

320
00:18:22,110 --> 00:18:23,790
and Sha Pingwei

321
00:18:24,550 --> 00:18:26,510
really love each other like they said.

322
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:30,310
I also did this for the country.

323
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,480
Yuan Buqu had rejected the marriage

324
00:18:33,310 --> 00:18:36,310
when he was guarding the border.

325
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:38,350
Now, he returns in triumph.

326
00:18:38,510 --> 00:18:40,480
If he chooses to marry the princess

327
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:43,070
and abandons his wife for his future,

328
00:18:43,920 --> 00:18:45,880
he is a heartless man.

329
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:49,030
How can he be trusted with the country?

330
00:18:51,350 --> 00:18:53,920
You're so considerate, Your Majesty.

331
00:18:56,820 --> 00:18:59,460
[Qi Residence]

332
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:05,790
Earlier, Bingyan

333
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:07,400
pretended to be
an elder brother from the Dus

334
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:08,400
and did me a solid.

335
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:10,440
I have to prepare a gift

336
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:11,400
and thank her properly.

337
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:13,030
I heard from Bingyan

338
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:15,590
that when she was married
to the General's Residence,

339
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:17,400
since the residence is at the border,

340
00:19:17,790 --> 00:19:20,400
the general didn't
hold a wedding ceremony for her.

341
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:23,000
Now, he's making it up for her.

342
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:25,030
Thank goodness. The general

343
00:19:25,270 --> 00:19:26,270
didn't fail her.

344
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:28,400
I'm gonna

345
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:31,200
make her a headband.

346
00:19:39,270 --> 00:19:40,550
What a shame

347
00:19:41,030 --> 00:19:43,030
I didn't learn embroidery well.

348
00:19:44,200 --> 00:19:45,440
I wanted to embroider

349
00:19:45,680 --> 00:19:47,400
a pair of wild geese on it.

350
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:48,960
But now I look at it,

351
00:19:50,510 --> 00:19:51,960
and they look like fat ducks.

352
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:56,160
Tell me,

353
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:58,880
since Bingyan is the general's wife,

354
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,350
wearing this on her head

355
00:20:00,350 --> 00:20:01,640
would be laughed at by people, right?

356
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:04,830
Your Ladyship,

357
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,270
just let me do it.

358
00:20:11,790 --> 00:20:13,640
You have a good will.

359
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:15,000
This gift

360
00:20:15,270 --> 00:20:16,720
represents your heart anyway.

361
00:20:19,030 --> 00:20:19,720
You're right.

362
00:20:20,030 --> 00:20:21,400
I tailored this piece of cloth

363
00:20:21,510 --> 00:20:22,920
and embroidered this flower.

364
00:20:23,790 --> 00:20:24,400
Yes.

365
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:26,350
Her Ladyship will definitely like it.

366
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:30,270
Here.

367
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,680
News of Du Bingyan came from the capital.

368
00:20:37,270 --> 00:20:38,070
What news?

369
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:40,480
The two of them
had reunited in the capital.

370
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:42,720
I thought
it was going to be a happy ending,

371
00:20:43,510 --> 00:20:45,240
but Her Majesty insisted that General Yuan

372
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:46,240
marry the princess.

373
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:47,720
General Yuan defied her decree

374
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:49,240
and was thrown into prison.

375
00:20:49,790 --> 00:20:50,750
How could it be like this?

376
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:53,270
Bingyan is so unlucky.

377
00:20:53,510 --> 00:20:54,510
First a princess,

378
00:20:54,510 --> 00:20:56,200
now there's a queen getting in the way.

379
00:20:56,510 --> 00:20:58,790
Then if the general divorces Her Ladyship

380
00:20:58,790 --> 00:20:59,960
to marry the princess,

381
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:02,030
what would happen to Her Ladyship?

382
00:21:02,030 --> 00:21:02,720
I dare him.

383
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:05,550
If Yuan Buqu fails Bingyan

384
00:21:05,550 --> 00:21:06,640
in order to be the emperor's son-in-law,

385
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:07,510
I'm gonna kill him!

386
00:21:09,350 --> 00:21:10,000
He won't.

387
00:21:10,510 --> 00:21:12,240
It's said that General Yuan

388
00:21:12,240 --> 00:21:14,070
attended the queen's banquet

389
00:21:14,070 --> 00:21:15,960
and rejected her decree openly.

390
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:16,960
He'd rather die than accept it.

391
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:18,720
Du Bingyan dressed like a maid

392
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:20,030
and stayed by General Yuan's side,

393
00:21:20,110 --> 00:21:21,920
refusing to be separated.

394
00:21:25,720 --> 00:21:26,680
Seems like

395
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:30,030
Bingyan has prepared
to die with the general.

396
00:21:32,110 --> 00:21:32,790
Alright.

397
00:21:33,030 --> 00:21:34,270
You should pack up.

398
00:21:34,270 --> 00:21:35,920
Let's set off to the capital right away

399
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:36,880
and find a way to rescue them.

400
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:39,000
Master and Ms. Shu are also on the way.

401
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:40,270
We'll meet in the capital

402
00:21:40,270 --> 00:21:41,240
to work things out together.

403
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:04,750
Tianlei and Yuhu are coming.

404
00:22:07,740 --> 00:22:10,300
[Guiyuan Inn]

405
00:22:17,790 --> 00:22:18,240
Tianlei.

406
00:22:18,240 --> 00:22:19,510
Master, Ms. Shu.

407
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:21,270
Come on in.

408
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:23,070
Your Highness,

409
00:22:23,480 --> 00:22:24,640
my uncle and aunt are here.

410
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:27,200
Greetings, Your Highness.

411
00:22:27,200 --> 00:22:27,960
Save it.

412
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:29,640
There's no need for that at moments like this.

413
00:22:30,110 --> 00:22:31,070
Pingwei told me

414
00:22:31,270 --> 00:22:32,920
that you're familiar with General Yuan.

415
00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:36,830
I used to be a surgeon
in General Yuan's camp.

416
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:37,920
As for these two,

417
00:22:38,030 --> 00:22:39,750
this is Third Young Master from Qi family,

418
00:22:39,750 --> 00:22:41,480
and this is Third Young Mistress.

419
00:22:41,480 --> 00:22:43,400
Me and Bingyan are sworn sisters.

420
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:46,920
By the way,

421
00:22:47,240 --> 00:22:49,590
have you visited Bingyan in the prison?

422
00:22:49,590 --> 00:22:50,240
How is she?

423
00:22:50,240 --> 00:22:51,350
Did anyone bully her?

424
00:22:54,550 --> 00:22:55,550
She's in
the Prison of the Ministry of Penalty.

425
00:22:55,790 --> 00:22:58,720
Unless there's a written permit
from His or Her Majesty,

426
00:22:59,030 --> 00:23:00,270
nobody can get in there.

427
00:23:05,550 --> 00:23:07,270
I've asked my father and cried.

428
00:23:07,550 --> 00:23:08,550
But he said

429
00:23:08,790 --> 00:23:10,030
mother did this for my own good,

430
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:11,110
and he wouldn't interfere.

431
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:15,000
My parents are such breaker-uppers.

432
00:23:17,550 --> 00:23:20,000
You're quite reasonable, though.

433
00:23:21,110 --> 00:23:22,880
I'll give up being the princess
at the worst.

434
00:23:23,350 --> 00:23:24,680
I'm gonna run away with Pingwei.

435
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,790
See how they're gonna do with me.

436
00:23:27,590 --> 00:23:28,350
It's just

437
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:30,830
that we've
implicated General Yuan and your sister.

438
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:32,790
We have to find a way
to infiltrate the prison

439
00:23:33,030 --> 00:23:34,400
and meet with them two.

440
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:37,200
We're outsiders

441
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:38,030
and are unaware of the details.

442
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:39,640
I'm afraid

443
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:40,960
it'll be hard for us to find the key.

444
00:23:41,270 --> 00:23:43,030
Maybe the two of them have some clues.

445
00:23:43,750 --> 00:23:44,510
You're right.

446
00:23:44,830 --> 00:23:46,920
We're circling aimlessly outside.

447
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:49,200
We have to see Bingyan as soon as possible

448
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:50,000
and discuss this with her.

449
00:23:52,270 --> 00:23:52,880
Lan,

450
00:23:53,750 --> 00:23:54,590
you're the princess.

451
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:56,480
Don't you have a way

452
00:23:56,480 --> 00:23:57,750
to bring us into that prison?

453
00:23:58,030 --> 00:24:00,070
I've cried in front
of my mother three times.

454
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:02,310
I'm really running out of ideas.

455
00:24:02,310 --> 00:24:03,750
What's the use of crying?

456
00:24:04,000 --> 00:24:05,790
When I was little, when dad prohibited me

457
00:24:05,790 --> 00:24:06,880
from doing anything,

458
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:08,200
I'd outsmart him

459
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:09,030
with various strategies.

460
00:24:09,030 --> 00:24:09,790
You gotta use your wits.

461
00:24:14,790 --> 00:24:15,590
You mentioned

462
00:24:16,310 --> 00:24:17,400
that in order to see Bingyan,

463
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:19,680
you gotta have a written permit, right?

464
00:24:22,270 --> 00:24:24,030
Then let's steal or snatch one.

465
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:25,160
Or forge one.

466
00:24:26,000 --> 00:24:26,510
Well...

467
00:24:26,510 --> 00:24:27,440
Are you serious...

468
00:24:27,550 --> 00:24:29,030
I think it's a good idea.

469
00:24:29,310 --> 00:24:30,480
Let's do this.

470
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:33,680
Then let's split up to take action.

471
00:24:34,680 --> 00:24:36,510
Me and Master go scout first

472
00:24:36,680 --> 00:24:38,310
to see how they patrol that prison.

473
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:39,480
Then we come up with a plan.

474
00:25:24,550 --> 00:25:25,750
Your Majesty, you're tired.

475
00:25:26,440 --> 00:25:27,550
Please go rest now.

476
00:25:31,880 --> 00:25:33,110
People say

477
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:36,680
that bloodlines are the most miraculous thing.

478
00:25:37,550 --> 00:25:38,480
In my opinion,

479
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:40,440
they are absolutely right.

480
00:25:41,750 --> 00:25:43,830
The princess is so like you.

481
00:25:44,310 --> 00:25:45,680
When you're young,

482
00:25:46,640 --> 00:25:48,960
you're also quite stubborn.

483
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:51,960
Back then,

484
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:55,590
I also cried and screamed

485
00:25:57,240 --> 00:25:58,830
to defy my parents' arrangement.

486
00:26:10,830 --> 00:26:12,920
Take my gold lotus out for me.

487
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:30,510
Your Majesty.

488
00:26:44,960 --> 00:26:46,350
After all these years,

489
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:49,960
this gold lotus still looks

490
00:26:50,790 --> 00:26:52,550
as shiny as before.

491
00:26:56,110 --> 00:26:56,830
Back then,

492
00:26:58,590 --> 00:27:01,200
when he gifted me this gold lotus,

493
00:27:05,310 --> 00:27:06,640
I felt like I was in a dream.

494
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:09,680
I thought happily

495
00:27:10,790 --> 00:27:12,270
that I'd finally found

496
00:27:12,830 --> 00:27:14,920
the one that I could depend on.

497
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:18,830
For him,

498
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:21,960
I put aside my dignity

499
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:25,400
and defied my parents.

500
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:26,680
I wanted to elope with him.

501
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:28,790
He promised

502
00:27:28,790 --> 00:27:31,350
to meet me
in the bamboo forest on the outskirts.

503
00:27:32,590 --> 00:27:34,200
But he didn't show up.

504
00:27:38,110 --> 00:27:40,350
I waited from dawn till dusk.

505
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:44,720
But he's nowhere to be seen.

506
00:27:54,510 --> 00:27:56,880
All men in the world are fickle.

507
00:27:59,590 --> 00:28:00,790
He must have run away

508
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:02,960
for fear of offending the royal family

509
00:28:04,350 --> 00:28:05,640
after hearing that I was drafted

510
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,590
for imperial concubines.

511
00:28:13,110 --> 00:28:14,920
I was blinded by love

512
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:16,350
and trusted a wrong man.

513
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:18,590
Now,

514
00:28:20,070 --> 00:28:22,270
I can never watch my daughter

515
00:28:22,640 --> 00:28:23,720
make the same mistake.

516
00:28:25,350 --> 00:28:26,750
I must find her

517
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:29,720
a reliable husband.

518
00:28:30,160 --> 00:28:33,720
I won't allow her
to be carried away by love

519
00:28:34,310 --> 00:28:35,310
and ruin her life.

520
00:28:36,310 --> 00:28:39,110
[Turns out mother is afraid]

521
00:28:40,030 --> 00:28:41,310
[that I'd be fooled and abandoned by men.]

522
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:45,270
[I misunderstood her.]

523
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:52,750
Come.

524
00:28:55,350 --> 00:28:56,030
Pingwei.

525
00:28:56,030 --> 00:28:56,680
Uncle.

526
00:28:57,590 --> 00:28:58,160
Anything?

527
00:29:01,270 --> 00:29:02,440
This is my mother's token.

528
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:03,590
I stole it without her knowing.

529
00:29:05,510 --> 00:29:06,440
You're not bad, huh?

530
00:29:07,070 --> 00:29:08,110
My Lan is the best.

531
00:29:08,550 --> 00:29:10,640
With the token,
things will be a lot easier.

532
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:22,510
Your Highness, please go no further.

533
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:25,270
How dare you?

534
00:29:25,270 --> 00:29:26,400
Are you blind?

535
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,720
How dare you stop me, the princess?

536
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:28,830
I dare not.

537
00:29:28,830 --> 00:29:30,110
It's just that this is a restricted prison.

538
00:29:30,110 --> 00:29:31,160
Nobody enters without a permit.

539
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:32,510
I'm just following my orders.

540
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:34,720
Please don't blame us, Your Highness.

541
00:29:37,200 --> 00:29:38,350
I'm here to visit General Yuan Buqu

542
00:29:38,350 --> 00:29:40,000
by order of my mother, the queen.

543
00:29:40,440 --> 00:29:41,880
My apologies. This way, Your Highness.

544
00:29:48,790 --> 00:29:49,750
It's all my fault, Bingyan.

545
00:29:51,070 --> 00:29:52,110
I couldn't protect you.

546
00:29:53,160 --> 00:29:54,200
We're husband and wife.

547
00:29:54,750 --> 00:29:56,070
We are supposed
to be in hardships together.

548
00:29:58,070 --> 00:29:59,680
What if Her Majesty wants to punish us...

549
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:01,160
You've offended Her Majesty

550
00:30:01,160 --> 00:30:02,920
for the sake of me.

551
00:30:03,550 --> 00:30:04,790
Since you treated me like this,

552
00:30:05,590 --> 00:30:08,200
I will follow you till the end.

553
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:14,400
Wish we could make it through.

554
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:27,920
Bingyan.

555
00:30:31,070 --> 00:30:32,000
Yuhu,

556
00:30:32,440 --> 00:30:33,590
how did you get in here?

557
00:30:34,350 --> 00:30:35,590
Princess brought us here.

558
