00:35:16,670 --> 00:35:18,070
Mother has made such a foolish decision.

626
00:35:18,670 --> 00:35:20,800
She broke up such a loving couple.

627
00:35:24,550 --> 00:35:25,880
Let's come up with a plan

628
00:35:26,150 --> 00:35:28,030
to get Bingyan and General Yuan
out of here.

629
00:35:30,070 --> 00:35:30,760
