to my mother back then.

633
00:35:37,590 --> 00:35:39,070
We can start with this.

634
00:35:39,590 --> 00:35:40,550
What is it?

635
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:42,030
When mother was young,

636
00:35:42,030 --> 00:35:43,400
